          - **Product descriptions:** Highlighted features relevant to the user
          - **Images and videos:** Showing products in contexts relevant to the user
          - **Navigation:** Personalized category ordering and search suggestions

          ## Technology Stack

          **Machine Learning Platform:**
          - **Frameworks:** TensorFlow, PyTorch for deep learning models
          - **Recommendation Libraries:** Surprise, LightFM for collaborative filtering
          - **Feature Engineering:** Apache Spark for large-scale data processing
          - **Model Serving:** TensorFlow Serving for real-time inference

          **Data Infrastructure:**
          - **Streaming:** Apache Kafka for real-time data ingestion
          - **Storage:** Amazon S3 for data lake, Redis for caching
          - **Processing:** Apache Spark for batch processing
          - **Analytics:** Amazon Redshift for data warehousing

          **Application Layer:**
          - **APIs:** FastAPI for high-performance recommendation serving
          - **Frontend:** React.js with real-time personalization
          - **CDN:** CloudFlare for global content delivery
          - **Monitoring:** DataDog for system monitoring and alerting

